* BUT IF YOU TAKE A GOOD LOOK
AT YOURSELF, YOU'RE GONNA SEE
THAT I'M STRONG NOW *

13:22.936 --> 13:24.371
* IT'S ALL ABOUT YOU *

13:24.437 --> 13:25.672
THE TOXIC TERROR!

13:25.738 --> 13:27.875
* I'M FINALLY
BREAKIN' THE NEWS *

13:27.941 --> 13:32.079
* YOU GOT TO GIVE IT ALL
UP TO SHOW ME THAT YOU'RE
GONNA BE STRONG NOW *

13:32.145 --> 13:35.115
Shaggy: COME ON, KIDS.
LET'S HIDE UP HERE!

13:35.916 --> 13:39.119
[BUBBLING]

13:40.387 --> 13:41.454
[CREAKING]

13:41.521 --> 13:42.489
WHOA!
WHOA!
WHOA!

13:42.555 --> 13:46.026
AAH!
AAH!
AAH!

13:48.061 --> 13:49.429
AAH!
AAH!
AAH!

13:49.496 --> 13:50.563
UHH!
UHH!
UHH!

13:50.630 --> 13:51.564
[CRASH]

13:51.631 --> 13:53.901
[SPLASH]

13:55.702 --> 13:57.337
[EVIL CHUCKLE]

13:59.206 --> 14:00.941
[BUBBLING]

14:01.008 --> 14:02.609
[ALL GASP FOR BREATH]

14:06.779 --> 14:09.682
Clyde: HEY, WHAT'S
GOING ON OUT THERE?

14:09.749 --> 14:11.418
BUT--BUT THIS CAN'T BE!

14:11.484 --> 14:13.086
NOT MY TANNING TOWER!

14:13.153 --> 14:17.557
NOW WHERE ARE ALL THE
GUESTS GONNA GET DEEP,
DARK, TROPIC TANS?

14:17.624 --> 14:19.993
YOU! YOU KIDS DID THIS!

14:20.060 --> 14:22.029
LIKE, NO WAY, MAN--
I MEAN, SIR!

14:22.095 --> 14:23.696
IT WAS THE TOXIC TERROR!

14:23.763 --> 14:26.099
STILL BLAMING THIS
ON GHOST STORIES.

14:26.166 --> 14:28.835
WELL, IT DOESN'T MATTER.
I'VE ALREADY MADE UP MY MIND.

14:28.902 --> 14:30.803
I'M SHUTTING DOWN
THIS SUMMER CAMP!

14:30.870 --> 14:33.006
WHAT?!
NO, PLEASE!
DON'T!

14:33.073 --> 14:34.774
WELL, YOU HAVE TO ADMIT,

14:34.841 --> 14:40.280
IT IS PRETTY UNSAFE
AROUND HERE, WHAT WITH
ALL THESE ACCIDENTS AND ALL.

14:40.347 --> 14:44.617
WE WOULDN'T WANT
ANYTHING TO HAPPEN TO
YOU CHILDREN, WOULD WE?

14:44.684 --> 14:47.154
JUST ADMIT IT!
YOU WANT TO TURN
OUR SUMMER CAMP

14:47.220 --> 14:49.056
INTO A PLACE
FOR GROWN-UPS!

14:49.122 --> 14:53.026
YOU CAN'T DO THIS!
CAMP IS OUR FAVORITE
PLACE IN THE WHOLE WORLD!

14:53.093 --> 14:56.363
REALLY? WOW, I'M...
I'M TOUCHED.

14:56.429 --> 14:58.598
NOT! NOW GET TO BED.

15:02.335 --> 15:05.172
I CAN'T BELIEVE CLYDE IS
GOING TO CLOSE THE CAMP.

15:05.238 --> 15:07.440
I CAN'T BELIEVE WE LET
DOWN SHAGGY AND SCOOBY.

15:07.507 --> 15:09.242
I REALLY THOUGHT
WE COULD HELP THEM OUT.

15:09.309 --> 15:13.346
MAYBE IN OUR HASTE
TO DECIPHER THIS
ENIGMA,

15:13.413 --> 15:15.482
UH...WE...

15:15.548 --> 15:16.683
SCREWED UP?

15:16.749 --> 15:17.884
EXACTLY.

15:17.951 --> 15:19.319
Shaggy: COME ON, GANG.

15:19.386 --> 15:21.854
Alex: SHAGGY? SCOOBY?
WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING?

15:21.921 --> 15:23.423
SOLVING THIS MYSTERY.

15:23.490 --> 15:26.559
GHOST OR NO GHOST,
THE CAMP IS OUR
FAVORITE PLACE, TOO.

15:26.626 --> 15:28.195
ALL RIGHT!

15:28.261 --> 15:31.764
NOW SCOOB AND I HAVE
SEEN A LOT OF MYSTERIES
BEING SOLVED.

15:31.831 --> 15:33.333
THAT'S GOT TO COUNT
FOR SOMETHING.

15:33.400 --> 15:36.069
AND THE FIRST THING
TO DO IF YOU WANT
TO SOLVE A MYSTERY

15:36.136 --> 15:39.106
IS LOCATE THE CREEPIEST,
SPOOKIEST PLACE AROUND.

15:39.172 --> 15:41.774
WELL, THAT'D BE
CABIN 13.

15:41.841 --> 15:45.912
MAN, I LIKED THIS WHOLE
SAVING CAMP IDEA BETTER
BEFORE YOU MENTIONED THAT.

15:45.979 --> 15:47.947
ME, TOO!

15:51.018 --> 15:53.320
OK, WE'RE HERE.
SO WHAT DO
WE DO NEXT

15:53.386 --> 15:54.921
TO SOLVE A
MYSTERY, SHAGGY?

15:54.988 --> 15:56.823
IS THERE A BASEMENT
TO THIS PLACE?

15:56.889 --> 15:59.892
SCOOB AND I ARE ALWAYS
BEING CHASED IN SPOOKY
BASEMENTS.

15:59.959 --> 16:00.827
THERE IS!

16:00.893 --> 16:03.230
OH, LUCKY US.

16:07.634 --> 16:09.136
HEY, WAIT A MINUTE.

16:09.202 --> 16:11.371
WE'RE IN THE BASEMENT
OF CABIN 13!

16:11.438 --> 16:13.173
LIKE, DID YOU
HAVE TO REMIND US?

16:13.240 --> 16:15.575
SCOOB AND I WERE IN
OUR HAPPY PLACES.

16:15.642 --> 16:17.510
I WAS IN ARUBA.

16:17.577 --> 16:19.446
NO, WHAT I'M SAYING IS
THAT WE'RE UNDERGROUND

16:19.512 --> 16:21.348
WHERE THE TOXIC DUMP
WOULD HAVE BEEN.

16:21.414 --> 16:24.184
BUT THERE IS
NO TOXIC WASTE HERE.

16:24.251 --> 16:26.353
THEN THE TOXIC TERROR
IS A FAKE!

16:26.419 --> 16:29.056
OH, YEAH? WELL, SOMEBODY
MIGHT WANT TO TELL HIM!

16:29.122 --> 16:30.923
[GROWLING]

16:30.990 --> 16:32.259
AAH!
AAH!

16:32.325 --> 16:33.460
[GROWLS]

16:33.526 --> 16:35.595
HE'S CUTTING THROUGH
THE SUPPORTING BEAMS!

16:35.662 --> 16:36.596
IS THAT BAD?

16:36.663 --> 16:37.897
[CREAKING]

16:37.964 --> 16:39.599
FORGET IT! I ANSWERED
MY OWN QUESTION.

16:39.666 --> 16:41.068
LIKE, RUN!

16:43.936 --> 16:45.305
UHH!
UHH!
UHH!

16:45.372 --> 16:46.339
[RUMBLING]

16:46.406 --> 16:47.407
WE MADE IT!

16:47.474 --> 16:49.809
YEAH, BUT SO DID
THE TOXIC TERROR!

16:49.876 --> 16:51.711
AAH!
AAH!
AAH!

16:51.778 --> 16:55.482
[GROWLS]

16:55.548 --> 16:58.551
HUH?

16:59.519 --> 17:01.521
RRARR!

17:01.588 --> 17:03.790
LIKE I DON'T
LOOK A GIFT MONSTER
IN THE MOUTH,

17:03.856 --> 17:05.625
BUT WHY DIDN'T HE
COME AFTER US?

17:05.692 --> 17:07.327
I THINK I KNOW.

17:07.394 --> 17:10.330
NOW, THESE ARE ALL
THE PLACES THE TOXIC
TERROR HAS ATTACKED.

17:10.397 --> 17:12.065
THE CORRAL WITH
THE NEW GOLF CARTS,

17:12.132 --> 17:13.533
THE NEW TANNING TOWER,

17:13.600 --> 17:15.435
CABIN 13 THAT CLYDE
HAD JUST REBUILT...

17:15.502 --> 17:17.670
AND IT DIDN'T
ATTACK US HERE

17:17.737 --> 17:18.838
IN THE OLD
TREE HOUSE.

17:18.905 --> 17:20.540
EXACTLY!

17:20.607 --> 17:21.941
EXACTLY WHAT?

17:22.008 --> 17:25.312
LOOKS LIKE WE'RE
GOING TO NEED A TRAP...
A MONSTER TRAP.

17:25.378 --> 17:27.046
LEAVE THAT
TO ME AND SCOOB.

17:27.114 --> 17:31.284
WE HAVE A LOT OF
EXPERIENCE WATCHING TRAPS
BEING PUT TOGETHER.

17:31.351 --> 17:34.521
YOU REALLY THINK THIS
IS GOING TO WORK?

17:34.587 --> 17:38.158
AS LONG AS SCOOB
AND I ARE LIVE BAIT,
IT CAN'T MISS.

17:38.225 --> 17:40.993
Scooby:
YEAH. LIVE BAIT.

17:41.060 --> 17:45.098
NOW ALL WE HAVE TO
DO IS STROLL AROUND
UNTIL HE SHOWS UP.

17:45.165 --> 17:46.933
LIKE, HEY,
IT ALREADY WORKED!

17:46.999 --> 17:50.870
WE'RE GOOD!
REAH!
TOO GOOD!

17:50.937 --> 17:52.372
[GROWLING]
YII!
AAH!

17:55.508 --> 17:57.544
HEY, WHAT ABOUT OUR TRAP?

17:57.610 --> 18:03.216
NO OFFENSE.
THE NET JUST SEEMED
A LITTLE LESS CRAZY.

18:04.117 --> 18:05.285
DENNIS?!
DENNIS?!

18:05.352 --> 18:08.421
HAH! I GOT YOU!
I FINALLY GOT YOU!

18:08.488 --> 18:10.257
YOU GUYS
WERE SO SCARED!

18:10.323 --> 18:13.059
YOU SHOULD HAVE
SEEN THE LOOKS
ON YOUR FACES!

18:13.126 --> 18:15.228
BUT DENNIS COULDN'T
HAVE DONE IT.

18:15.295 --> 18:16.463
IT DOESN'T
MAKE SENSE.

18:16.529 --> 18:17.964
ALL THE CLUES
POINTED TO--

18:18.030 --> 18:21.634
ZOINKS!
2 TOXIC TERRORS?

18:21.701 --> 18:22.869
RUN!

18:22.935 --> 18:24.571
[SNARLING AND GROWLING]

18:24.637 --> 18:27.106
[SCOOBY AND SHAGGY
WHIMPERING]

18:31.110 --> 18:34.147
YAAH!

18:34.214 --> 18:37.250
OOH! AAH! OOH! YAH!

18:37.317 --> 18:41.020
HA HA HA HA!
NEVER DOUBT THE POWER
OF A CRAZY TRAP!

18:41.087 --> 18:42.889
FRED SURE
WOULD BE PROUD.

18:42.955 --> 18:43.956
WHO'S FRED?

18:44.023 --> 18:44.991
GOT ME.

18:45.057 --> 18:48.228
OK. LET'S TRY THIS AGAIN.

18:48.928 --> 18:49.796
GREY?!
GREY?!

18:49.862 --> 18:51.063
I'M SORRY, SHAGGY.

18:51.130 --> 18:53.666
I WASN'T AFTER
YOU AND SCOOBY.

18:53.733 --> 18:56.936
I WAS TRYING TO
DESTROY THE NEW
BUILDINGS AROUND CAMP.

18:57.003 --> 18:59.639
YOU TWO WERE JUST
ALWAYS IN THE WRONG
PLACE AT THE WRONG TIME.

18:59.706 --> 19:03.009
MAN, THAT'S LIKE
THE STORY OF OUR LIVES.

19:03.075 --> 19:04.377
YOU SAID IT!

19:04.444 --> 19:06.679
WELL, I WOULD HAVE
GOTTEN AWAY WITH IT

19:06.746 --> 19:09.081
IF IT WEREN'T FOR
THOSE MEDDLING KIDS
IN YOUR CABIN.

19:09.148 --> 19:11.784
BUT WHAT IS THIS
CRAZY GLOWING GOOP?

19:11.851 --> 19:15.522
THIS IS THE TOXIC MOSS
I WAS TELLING EVERYONE
ABOUT IN NATURE CLASS.

19:15.588 --> 19:17.457
Shaggy: SO DENNIS
MADE HIS OWN TOXIC SUIT

19:17.524 --> 19:19.158
RRAR!
BECAUSE HE WANTED
TO SCARE US.

19:19.226 --> 19:21.461
HE SAW THE MONSTER
WAS THE ONLY THING
THAT DID THAT.

19:21.528 --> 19:23.863
BUT GREY, WHY DID YOU
DO ALL THIS?

19:23.930 --> 19:25.565
TO SCARE CLYDE AWAY.

19:25.632 --> 19:29.135
SHAGGY, PEOPLE ALWAYS
WANT TO CHANGE THINGS
IN THE WORLD.

19:29.202 --> 19:31.338
THEY SAY IT'S TO MAKE
PROGRESS.

19:31.404 --> 19:36.243
BUT SOMETIMES
THINGS ARE PERFECT
JUST THE WAY THEY ARE.

19:36.309 --> 19:38.177
THIS CAMP DIDN'T
NEED TO CHANGE.

19:38.245 --> 19:43.783
HMM. LIKE, CLYDE STILL
HASN'T SEEN THE TOXIC
TERROR, HAS HE?

19:46.519 --> 19:47.454
[TYPING]

19:47.520 --> 19:48.488
[GROWLS]

19:48.555 --> 19:49.889
AAH!

19:52.792 --> 19:53.893
[GROWLS]

19:53.960 --> 19:55.795
AAH!

19:56.696 --> 19:57.697
[GROWLS]

19:57.764 --> 19:58.931
AAH!

19:58.998 --> 20:00.767
[GROWLS]

20:00.833 --> 20:02.735
[GROWLS]

20:02.802 --> 20:04.537
[GROWLS]

20:04.604 --> 20:06.773
[GROWLS]

20:06.839 --> 20:08.074
[GROWLS]

20:08.140 --> 20:10.877
AAH!

20:10.943 --> 20:12.712
[CRASH]

20:12.779 --> 20:14.247
AAH!

20:14.314 --> 20:15.915
HA HA HA HA!
HA HA HA HA!

20:15.982 --> 20:18.818
[LAUGHTER AND TALKING]

20:22.589 --> 20:24.757
NOW THIS IS MORE LIKE IT,
RIGHT, SCOOBY-DOO?

20:24.824 --> 20:27.327
SCOOBY!

20:27.394 --> 20:28.227
SCOOBY-DOOBY-DOO!

20:28.295 --> 20:30.697
[SPLASH]
